 he takes the chicken first, then the fox and grain stay on the original side\u3002 When he returns back to get the fox or grain, the chicken might eat the grain or fox\u3002 \n\nThis seems complicated. Maybe there's a better way\u3002 \n\nScenario 2: Farmer takes the grain first\u3002 Then, the fox and chicken"}, {"v": 6, "s": 0, "text": "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n"}, {"v": 7, "s": 0, "text": "\n\n\u7684\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a9d\u9e21\u7a